{"tid":849791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【紅海行動FF？支那護照最強後盾？】3名支那人在中非被打死   支方遲遲未表態","createTime":"2018-10-06T03:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T05:29:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c41b4275f1bb07575554e357a8553477017c8a9f","tid":849791,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:31:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181006/58762640\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58762640&d=QiaWgH%2FHQ409H7xcLwSKa4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=387b30d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58762640&h=1c7f15e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181006/58762640</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181006/large/1538794644_83f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181006%2Flarge%2F1538794644_83f2.jpg&h=c055d9af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中非共和國發生支那公民被暴打致死事件，至少3人被居民襲擊喪生，另有3名支那籍男子重傷。北京政府近來多次塑造全面保護公民在海外權益的形象，令外界關注支方反應，不過支那外交部及駐當地大使館均未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n3名男死者是在周四於當地西南部一個礦區被打死，事緣一個約由10名支那人組成的團隊招募青少年領袖，當地議會第二副議長的弟弟納科埃（Ignace Dimbele-Nakoe）充當導遊帶團隊前往一個金礦，然而一行人乘搭的船隻翻側，納科埃的屍體後來被發現。<br />\n<br />\n當團隊回村報警時，村民指責他們令納科埃溺斃，以棍棒毆打他們，當時現場只有少數警察。襲擊導致3死3重傷，傷者仍然留醫，而3具遺體就已用飛機運往首都班基（Bangui）。<br />\n<br />\n支那官方近來加緊保護公民在海外權益，早前有公民在瑞典旅遊時因在酒店外哭鬧遭警方驅離，事件被支方提升至外交爭議層面，支那駐瑞典大使館與支那外交部亦多次就事件表態。"},{"pid":"0621950def46cf1d0e0e5cfe1f33978e1c6332fe","tid":849791,"uid":18955,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:33:24.000Z","msg":"美國：將現實故事搬上大銀幕<br />\n某國：用大銀幕散播虛構故事"},{"pid":"b7176790045898d10ce8832ad2566df7bcaaec93","tid":849791,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0621950def46cf1d0e0e5cfe1f33978e1c6332fe","tid":849791,"uid":18955,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:33:24.000Z","msg":"美國：將現實故事搬上大銀幕<br />\n某國：用大銀幕散播虛構故事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:35:43.000Z","msg":"紅海行動99.99%虛構扮真實, <br />\n<br />\n竟然可以去角逐獎項<br />\n<br />\n都可算係無恥"},{"pid":"96af397c296edea3e6c30848d41b9512d6acce64","tid":849791,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:37:43.000Z","msg":"俾左600億美元竟然連殺中国人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇怕要加多600億<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358a8066c99fc61a5f31b708e49509e1cfca9517","tid":849791,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:42:28.000Z","msg":"你班尼加PK了, <br />\n激嬲戰狼了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de77ef701af650301683386c69ebafb4705b5a7","tid":849791,"uid":26601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"沒事兒 沒事兒"},{"pid":"69499cee9dfff958285a86e071b0901493dfccaf","tid":849791,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"有分析認為<br />\n中國或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"522f28e060579288a85b1e9e262062697505d238","tid":849791,"uid":52358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:22:26.000Z","msg":"被打到從黃皮膚變成黑皮膚<br />\n因為死者係黑皮膚 唔算中国人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1acaa10b428dc75d9ef743657ed6d722374dbfb9","tid":849791,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:23:57.000Z","msg":"蟔&gt;蝗"},{"pid":"a3f3337527b7c8988b0a53d8f1f2a80e039c6139","tid":849791,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9de8ae93bb539261980f8eb9aab80913dd0546","tid":849791,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:25:39.000Z","msg":"一帶一路掠緊水架嘛,你死你事啦"},{"pid":"9661e9ad55dba0bd76457e3a7a532ccfc173668d","tid":849791,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:25:53.000Z","msg":"如果係港豬....<br />\n你打人就係唔文明<br />\n<br />\n中非又高香港豬十分"},{"pid":"a2931dee2e0810af6377259b76fb4495dcbff6c3","tid":849791,"uid":31389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://world.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2017/0810/MAIN201708101047000094061677205.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fworld.people.com.cn%2FNMediaFile%2F2017%2F0810%2FMAIN201708101047000094061677205.jpg&h=1ef2ea58&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}